==================================================
FLOW 1: LANDING PAGE
==================================================

START PROGRAM

DISPLAY Landing Page
SHOW website logo "SavorScync"
SHOW welcome message
SHOW "Get Started" button

WHEN user clicks "Get Started" button
NAVIGATE to "Log-in.html" page
END WHEN


==================================================
FLOW 2: LOGIN / REGISTER PAGE
==================================================

DISPLAY Login & Register Page
SHOW logo, title, and two tabs: [Login] [Create Account]

--------------------------
CASE A: User wants to Register
--------------------------
WHEN user clicks "Create Account" tab
SWITCH view to Registration Form
END WHEN

WHEN user submits Registration Form
READ input: Full Name, Email, Password, Confirm Password

IF any field is empty THEN
SHOW error: "Please fill in all fields."
ELSE IF Password ≠ Confirm Password THEN
SHOW error: "Passwords do not match."
ELSE IF Email already exists in saved data THEN
SHOW error: "An account with this email already exists."
ELSE
SAVE new user data to browser storage
SHOW success message: "Account created successfully!"
SHOW button: "Go to Login"
END IF
END WHEN

WHEN user clicks "Go to Login" button
SWITCH view to Login Form
END WHEN


--------------------------
CASE B: User wants to Login
--------------------------
WHEN user clicks "Login" tab
SWITCH view to Login Form
END WHEN

WHEN user submits Login Form
READ input: Email, Password

IF any field is empty THEN
SHOW error: "Please fill in all fields."
ELSE
SEARCH saved user data for matching Email AND Password
IF match found THEN
SHOW welcome message: "Welcome back, [User Name]!"
SHOW link/button: "Go to Main Site"
ELSE
SHOW error: "Invalid email or password."
END IF
END IF
END WHEN

==================================================
FLOW 3: MAIN SITE (Food Ordering Page)
==================================================

WHEN user clicks "Go to Main Site" link/button
NAVIGATE to main website page (Food Ordering System)

DISPLAY Main Site
SHOW header with navigation: Menu, Cart, Order, Feedback, Contact
SHOW food menu list with items, prices and "Add to Cart" buttons
SHOW cart section to view selected items and total price
SHOW order form for delivery details
SHOW feedback form
SHOW contact information

ENABLE all functions:
- Add item to cart
- Remove item from cart
- Auto-update cart count and total
- Submit order and show success
- Submit feedback and show thank you message
END WHEN

END PROGRAM
